content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 319.302 - Hash

State Regulations

Hash shall contain not less than 35 percent of meat
computed on the weight of the cooked and trimmed meat. The weight of the cooked
meat used in this calculation shall not exceed 70 percent of the weight of the
uncooked fresh meat. Notes
